[h2 id=Wiki
 
	" Wiki
	$LF
]h2
[p 
	"If you want to help with wiki pages, you will need to be an 
	[a class=intlink href=/EditorGuidelines 
		"editor
	]a
	".  If you have a project in mind, contact 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users 
		"an admin assistant or site admin
	]a
	" with details and you will probably be granted editor access.
	$LF
]p
[h3 id=VariouspageTODOs
 
	" Various page TODOs
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		" Many pages which 
		[a class=intlink href=/Ref.exe?page=TODO 
			"refer
		]a
		" to this TODO page have changes which the editors feel could be made. Be aware that some pages (such as 
		(__wikiLink|/ArticleIndex|ArticleIndex)
		") link to TODO but not for this reason.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 id=Adopttheorphans
 
	" Adopt the orphans
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		" Pages with no links to them, as well as non-existent pages linked from somewhere are found in 
		(__wikiLink|/WikiOrphans|Wiki Orphans)
		"; links to these pages should be added elsewhere.  This is an ongoing problem.  It is HIGHLY encouraged that all staff & editors participate in keeping these Orphans fixed.
		$LF
		[ul 
			[li 
				" Also consult 
				[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/sgrunt 
					"sgrunt
				]a
				"'s 
				[a class=intlink href=/Sgrunt/PseudoOrphans 
					"pseudo-orphans
				]a
				" list for pages with few links pointing to them.
				$LF
			]li
		]ul
	]li
]ul
